data.description: Highly desired neighborhood and a nice corner lot are only the beginning for this nice vinyl sided 3 bedroom/1.5 bath charmer. Enjoy the nice vinyl fenced yard while hanging out on the rear patio. 2 Car detached garage, large living room with a real wood burning fireplace to keep you cozy during those chilly evenings and a huge home office. Formal dining room off the nicely appointed kitchen, there is a recently updated 1/2 bath off the kitchen and laminate floors on the first level  and natural hardwood floors throughout the second floor bedrooms and hallways. Many possible uses for the 20'x12' Bonus room in the partially finished attic. 3 year old roof and many newer vinyl replacement windows and a brand new water heater.
